    <Description>Shifters are a basic Eberron race with notable Lycanthropic ancestry.
They cannot transform entirely into animals, but can shift parts of their bodies
to be animal-like for short periods of time. In DDO, this Shifting has
similarities (and statistical connections to) Raging.

Depending on sub-race selection, Shifters excel at Defense/Tanking or WIS-based
casting.</Description>
