    <Feat>
      <Name>Beasthide Shifter</Name>
      <Description>Passive: +1 Constitution
Active: Activate this Shifter ability to shift your form, granting you a +4 Rage bonus to
Armor Class and Constitution, a +2 Morale bonus to Fortitude saves, and a -2 penalty to Wisdom.
When the form ends, however, you will lose the hit points granted by increased Constitution
and become fatigued. Your form will last for 30 seconds plus an additional amount of time
based on your Constitution. You can prematurely end your form by using the Dismiss Rage
feat. This shares charges with Barbarian's Rage feat, and anything that grants bonuses while
Raging will grant bonuses with this. Shifting your form in this way prevents Spellcasting,
and prevents use of other abilities that cannot be used while Raging.</Description>
